OL,5, A New Zealand tour company has been    
OL,6, found guilty of not "minimising risk"  
OL,7, to 22 people who died in the 2019 White
OL,8, Island volcano disaster.               
OL,10,FJudge Evangelos Thomas criticised what 
OL,11,Fhe said were "astonishing failures" by 
OL,12,FWhakaari Management Limited (WML) -    
OL,13,Fwhich licenses tours to the island.    
OL,15,FThe case is the largest action of its  
OL,16,Fkind brought by New Zealand's          
OL,17,Fregulator, Worksafe NZ.                
OL,19,FThe company faces up to NZ$1.5m        
OL,20,F($928,000; #724,000) in fines.         
